打，都咪話唔勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁marvel有咩一線？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nMarvel 1線咪就係賣左電影版權出去嘅蜘蛛仔 x-men 同神奇4俠</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n神奇四俠係高知名度同第一個超級英雄家庭，其實好難話係近年既一線，你睇Marvel夠疆cut咗F4主刊就知<br />\n就算話係為咗逼Fox放返版權，又唔見佢cut鳩xmen同變種人？<br />\n雖然劇情同大事件參與度都高<br />\n<br />\n利申：F4 fan</blockquote><br />\nF4無一線好耐啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁係因為近年d戲拍得閪<br />\n其他太好<br />\n以前真係一線<br />\nF4算係marvel白銀時代第一套，第一個團體英雄</blockquote><br />\nf4入面個火人好似仲要係marvel第二個超級英雄</blockquote><br />\n唔係第二個,好似直程係第一個"},{"pid":"1d6121019e9b321abdc505acc733a030e86cf8e0","tid":333301,"uid":124951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T19:21:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>留意返，我講iron man紅係指mcu之後，唔好曲解我</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nMarvel 係電影上面就係用班2線superhero 撳住你dc班一線黎打，都咪話唔勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁marvel有咩一線？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nMarvel 1線咪就係賣左電影版權出去嘅蜘蛛仔 x-men 同神奇4俠</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n神奇四俠係高知名度同第一個超級英雄家庭，其實好難話係近年既一線，你睇Marvel夠疆cut咗F4主刊就知<br />\n就算話係為咗逼Fox放返版權，又唔見佢cut鳩xmen同變種人？<br />\n雖然劇情同大事件參與度都高<br />\n<br />\n利申：F4 fan</blockquote><br />\nF4無一線好耐啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁係因為近年d戲拍得閪<br />\n其他太好<br />\n以前真係一線<br />\nF4算係marvel白銀時代第一套，第一個團體英雄</blockquote><br />\nf4入面個火人好似仲要係marvel第二個超級英雄</blockquote><br />\n唔係第二個,好似直程係第一個</blockquote><br />\n唔好意思...第一個好似係Namor<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb42ef763c0d59c160ecdf562976f0857181bc81","tid":333301,"uid":20032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T19:36:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>本身唔太鍾意iron man 可能因為漫畫關係<br />\n而家見到d小朋友講到iron man咁正面就好燥</blockquote><br />\n但你都要理解啊巴打<br />\n<br />\n始終係新宇宙嚟<br />\n<br />\n你都唔會話見到injustice 大超咁仆街而嬲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢地係講緊mcu ironman，有d好有d衰啦"},{"pid":"c7b787b6230d46a9cf9be94e30c0a94e188df7f7","tid":333301,"uid":17368,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T22:37:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\nMarvel 1線咪就係賣左電影版權出去嘅蜘蛛仔 x-men 同神奇4俠</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n神奇四俠係高知名度同第一個超級英雄家庭，其實好難話係近年既一線，你睇Marvel夠疆cut咗F4主刊就知<br />\n就算話係為咗逼Fox放返版權，又唔見佢cut鳩xmen同變種人？<br />\n雖然劇情同大事件參與度都高<br />\n<br />\n利申：F4 fan</blockquote><br />\nF4無一線好耐啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁係因為近年d戲拍得閪<br />\n其他太好<br />\n以前真係一線<br />\nF4算係marvel白銀時代第一套，第一個團體英雄</blockquote><br />\nf4入面個火人好似仲要係marvel第二個超級英雄</blockquote><br />\n唔係第二個,好似直程係第一個</blockquote><br />\n唔好意思...第一個好似係Namor<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n第二個人嚟，只係同名，第一個火人無得熄火，要長期套住個罩"},{"pid":"71038d5cca8069332bdd0b2bd942689fe3c8d051","tid":333301,"uid":84369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T22:45:34.000Z","msg":"自己係睇以前JL個卡通片識<br />\nSpiderman紅夠貼地 電影又出得好 （頭兩集）<br />\n<br />\n依家繼呢三個之後我覺得係狼人 iron man同美隊"},{"pid":"e054b2005e28e16f59be7974e009557e4ff48fd7","tid":333301,"uid":64191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T22:56:22.000Z","msg":"當時tvb成日播spiderman, batman卡通，好難唔識<br />\n但超人我係因為iq博士先識"},{"pid":"e1a243db971b6193a768a6db933805a15c9fd54c","tid":333301,"uid":94516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T22:59:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\nMarvel 1線咪就係賣左電影版權出去嘅蜘蛛仔 x-men 同神奇4俠</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n神奇四俠係高知名度同第一個超級英雄家庭，其實好難話係近年既一線，你睇Marvel夠疆cut咗F4主刊就知<br />\n就算話係為咗逼Fox放返版權，又唔見佢cut鳩xmen同變種人？<br />\n雖然劇情同大事件參與度都高<br />\n<br />\n利申：F4 fan</blockquote><br />\nF4無一線好耐啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁係因為近年d戲拍得閪<br />\n其他太好<br />\n以前真係一線<br />\nF4算係marvel白銀時代第一套，第一個團體英雄</blockquote><br />\nf4入面個火人好似仲要係marvel第二個超級英雄</blockquote><br />\n唔係第二個,好似直程係第一個</blockquote><br />\n唔好意思...第一個好似係Namor<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n第二個人嚟，只係同名，第一個火人無得熄火，要長期套住個罩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nsuperman 首次登場於《動作漫畫》#1（<span style=\"color: red;\">1938</span>年6月）<br />\n<br />\nNamor <span style=\"color: red;\">1939</span>年首次登場於漫威漫畫<br />\n<br />\nNamor 係marvel第一個<br />\n<br />\n個個火人係marvel第二個，係CA1的展覽，tony老豆show車個度其實有出現到"},{"pid":"ba122c5efd3d51f7d3734d6993ea2ae095904af3","tid":333301,"uid":94516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T23:03:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>超人同batman係最早的英雄<br />\n基本上佢地就係始祖<br />\n咁點唔紅姐<br />\n一個第一個超級英雄<br />\n一個第一個無超能力的超級英雄<br />\n<br />\n正常第一個就會出名架啦<br />\n因為你代表緊個樣野<br />\n<br />\nSpiderman就有人講左</blockquote><br />\nBatman唔清楚<br />\n但係邊個話你知superman係第一個superhero<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nFor the most literal answer, comics began as just reprinted collections of the comic strips that ran in newspapers. The first time one such book contained a costumed hero with superhuman abilities was Action Comics #1, with <span style=\"color: red;\">Superman</span>, in <span style=\"color: red;\">1938</span>.<br />\n<br />\n[url]<a href=\"https://www.quora.com/What-was-the-first-comic-book-superhero\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.quora.com%2FWhat-was-the-first-comic-book-superhero&d=Zx5i35Pc1Ra68Zgd49OhzgRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=038b0163\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.quora.com/What-was-the-first-comic-book-superhero</a><br />\n[/url]<br />\n<br />\n1938年，名為《動作漫畫》的連環漫畫雜誌首次展示了腳蹬紅靴子的超人把一輛汽車高高舉過頭頂的形象"},{"pid":"3e0916c1243371f9dda7c0b2dc7e53359ce4b3df","tid":333301,"uid":57462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T23:50:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\nF4無一線好耐啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁係因為近年d戲拍得閪<br />\n其他太好<br />\n以前真係一線<br />\nF4算係marvel白銀時代第一套，第一個團體英雄</blockquote><br />\nf4入面個火人好似仲要係marvel第二個超級英雄</blockquote><br />\n唔係第二個,好似直程係第一個</blockquote><br />\n唔好意思...第一個好似係Namor<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n第二個人嚟，只係同名，第一個火人無得熄火，要長期套住個罩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nsuperman 首次登場於《動作漫畫》#1（<span style=\"color: red;\">1938</span>年6月）<br />\n<br />\nNamor <span style=\"color: red;\">1939</span>年首次登場於漫威漫畫<br />\n<br />\nNamor 係marvel第一個<br />\n<br />\n個個火人係marvel第二個，係CA1的展覽，tony老豆show車個度其實有出現到</blockquote><br />\nhumantorch?"},{"pid":"aac53f45f609a077481faeb3